OK, I couldn't wait for it to come on and I was not disappointed at all. Excellent writing, excellent acting by all members of the cast. Story line totally different and shocking. I loved it. We need to see more writing like this, what a pleasure to try and figure out what's going to happen next.

So sick and tired of the boring "white male or white female leads with the same old story line.

Ms. Davis said that she "wanted something to take her out of her comfort zone and this program does just that. I also like the idea of TGIH with the two preceding shows. I can't wait for Thursday nights to come now. Yeaaaaaaaaaay